antasystoriesforum.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ryvian>Ryvian</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Warlord of Delnor</span><br>  Posts: 180<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/4/02 5:08 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm7.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=12.topic&index=12>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The Adventures of Rillen and the Gang</span><hr size=1> Somewhat upset that his song did not lighten the mood, Paren muttered to himself, &quot;Only if you can catch me.&quot; and with that he sat down with a hurmp. &quot;This is going to be a long day I just know it. Why in the name of all that is good and holy do I get stuck with the most unhumored of company that they can not take a small joke...&quot; Looking at the anger on each of their faces he decided to just go back to humming, maybe then they couldn't get mad if they didn't hear the words...<br>
